Global Variable# NSMetadataUbiquitousItemDownloadingStatusNotDownloaded

iOS 7.0+iPadOS 7.0+Mac Catalyst 13.1+macOS 10.9+tvOS 9.0+visionOS 1.0+watchOS 2.0+

```
let NSMetadataUbiquitousItemDownloadingStatusNotDownloaded: String
```

## [Discussion](/documentation/foundation/nsmetadataubiquitousitemdownloadingstatusnotdownloaded#Discussion)

A string used as the value for [`NSMetadataUbiquitousItemPercentUploadedKey`](/documentation/foundation/nsmetadataubiquitousitempercentuploadedkey) to indicate that this item has not been downloaded yet.

You can use [`startDownloadingUbiquitousItem(at:)`](/documentation/foundation/filemanager/startdownloadingubiquitousitem(at:)) to download the item.
